    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Compulsion)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The subject feels as if its body is being torn apart by and feels excruciating pain. The subject suffers a -4 penalty to attack rolls, weapon damage rolls, skill numerous sword slashes. It sees its skin being torn open checks and ability checks.<br><br>This technique can be dispelled, but there is a 50% chance that any dispel attempt will fail.</p>\n\n\n\n",
